{"tid":1602752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"走嗰陣請不要打斜跑，kick死人架","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:48:10.000Z","uid":274336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbed7b9e85515da9028da0ecf5ea751a4fe8d3a","tid":1602752,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"如題，成日出去做運動見到啲人打斜跑，想kick撚死我咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇路唔好搶人條線跑先得架，幾次差啲kick到仆街，好彩夠平衡力，唔係全力跑緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑步都要留意周圍架！！一陣有壞人就唔好啦，見到仲有人打斜跑去壞人到，好彩捉住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不完美，可接受，要改善。<br />\n<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a42993704f3791ee16a1e58c9e7e91a6e8183a","tid":1602752,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7465375a0d9fa7029f564a4474174c92159587a","tid":1602752,"uid":226085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:48:10.000Z","msg":"有一次係銅鑼灣跑緊 被個手足斜cut<br />\n差啲仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}